8 An Act relating to public finance; amending Section
3, Chapter 348, O.S.L. 2022 (62 O.S. Supp. 2024,
9 Section 2021), which relates to the Oklahoma Disaster
Mitigation and Recovery Matching Fund; modifying
10 provisions related to allocation of funds; and
